<br>
Standing mana regen = 1 mana/tick<br>
Sitting mana regen (@ 252 med skill) = 21 mana/tick<br>
<br>
So at max med skill, sitting gains you 20 mana/tick, since all the other buffs/items/effects we're discussing here work whether sitting or standing.<br>
